<p align="justify" line-height=21px>
This page shows the taxonomic profile from a single run of the HMP2 workflow.  Each run is comprised of a set 
of data that has been uploaded to the HMP2 servers.  Once there, it is filtered for quality and error checked
for completeness.  After the QC phase, the data is run on a specific Anadama pipeline.  After the pipeline
completes, the output files can be accumulated into several highlevel charts shown below.  For contact information
regarding the results and the workflow process, please search <a href=https://ibdmdb.org/enrollment> here.</a>
</p>
